'''UWARS''' - Universal Water Activated Release System- is a [[Personal flotation device|life-preserving system]] made by [[Conax Florida Corporation]].  The UWARS is attached to a buckle or [[safety harness|harness]] that, when submerged in water, releases a harness and thus prevents [[drowning]].

